{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"反虑不漏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM74ylahuHyEkPRj7ib29Ujem2BJhgPtUSxzibrLQ75KGAjHwkQJtSuubnYiaH0ia8zEnplJicLSnDOrRKibT7uGdHYAO29Rvk4VKP9nA/0","content":"<p>顶头上司的关键业务：对工程进行管理，重点在安全、质量和进度方面。</p><p>发现了：领导靠嘴巴子管工程，我靠笔杆子管工程。</p><p>提升计划：人治大于法治的行业，还能说什么，领导说了算，当然自己也得多动脑子，避免被当枪使，安全是第一位的，明哲保身。业余时间提升自己，找找未来的出路，这不找到RISE探索出路了。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9080,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492788524000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"澄澄","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcIeU77F6ia2oKMEQh6f6uZmNicQQnscrxHFdtzmicLUwRB2LE6j3F3WhOApfyS0NSFN7qlvfPK2JDVF5p5ANxDPUHS/0","content":"一、顶头上司关键业务<div>1.了解公司战略，摸清上级领导当前及近三年工作规划和每阶段工作重点;</div><div>2.带领团队实现领导意图;</div><div>3.跨部门沟通协调，促进各项政策落地。</div><div>二.与自己关键业务相比</div><div>1相同相通的:一定了解公司战略，高效完成自己关键业务促进战略落地;</div><div>2不同的是:单兵作战和团队系统完成，善用外部资源很重要。</div><div>三.提升计划</div><div>1紧扣战略，积极主动完成自己关键业务;</div><div>2加强跨部门沟通，融入业务，更好地理解战略，促进战略落地。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9040,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492785232000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"晓雨","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny682vYQ4NQHPvicvZGZJwpJtEWDUKyrJ3iaoM8j6zKKVoxp0HrlwUMxFN7PyjtBypkhUswYPcF1OJ1RRDuugM3gU0B/0","content":"顶头上司的关键业务是制定发展规划，与我相比动脑和应酬的地方比我多，我必须通过多学习和多思考的方式提升自己的大脑，给出电销发展的建设性意见。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9024,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492783437000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"永烨妈妈","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bUaKkQxYKNkV3tONQv3D3aP4trJrSIjxhwINwVnWvCUMTWxPV8p6MneicntibMdUvHHrVb71vvvggdX4tKjTLx97/0","content":"上司的工作任务是：保证公司资金到位，合理避税，我的任务是：辅助贷款，做贷款收尾工作，保重公司不踩法律红线。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8754,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492712199000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"肖伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FXdnOMf95S97bMklhD3pPgAic1mrkwF4LJSQ3oIqRJjLvPRxNXRq2KU57AE3WQAEm4JYz78buibxsX/0","content":"<div>上司工作</div><div>1、提高本部运营</div><div>2、提高本部利润</div><div>自身关键业务</div><div>1、车线成本管控</div><div>2、人员薪酬绩效</div><div>3、对接总部行政工作</div><div>发现:</div><div>1、成本管控作为提利的方式之一，是重点</div><div>2、绩效评定与考核是为本部储备人才的一种手段，不能直接见效</div><div>3、对接总部行政工作，推进执行力与标准化也是减少培训成本的一种方式，需要慢慢改进。</div><div>总结，成本管控为首，绩效与标准化执行都是针对提升整体素质降低成本的一种方式，但效果并不明显，需要将主要精力用在成本管控上。无奈，总部标准化执行性项目占用了我太多时间。</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8752,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492711206000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jane Chen","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJiag5nIltO6gSzJ79iac9oVws6icW0K6OMdS1A6lD1ZPibHkUQ2SBDqXGfzRMEjv5PMUClTkszspOdQRA08ta0wT5s/0","content":"顶头上司的关键业务：<div>1.分析受众需求找到合适的项目<br><div>2.管理项目进度、预算、质量</div></div><div>3.管理团队</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8560,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492686401000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"如如不动","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPwbASLcicF5LZfAmia0twbsk2utgDpT5ar14ibFRJ0HibzQAymfRr3kBujHweV06lTe5VLfKiaRJSN5X/0","content":"顶头上司是管理层，要时间熬。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8553,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492685616000,"priority":0,"perfect":n