serName":"Grace谷","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icye0y15ytCp7Be1mStPR9VjXsjtBDNWKpmdicgcr7efY9cKpcJmqb7n6x2pkKviaE67VjB35fgjR4Q/0","content":"上司关键业务：<div>1、国内国外市场分析判断</div><div>2、对比我们产品与国际品牌产品差距</div><div>3、制定市场开发策略</div><div>我的关键业务：</div><div>1、收集国际贸易信息，了解国际贸易动向，为市场开启做决策依据。</div><div>2、利用数据平台和分析工具，通过量化信息判断海外市场可进入的可行性。</div><div>3、涉及到产品海外销售的认证事宜。</div><div>差距：</div><div>1、掌握的信息量差距大，做判断和决策的速度及精准差距大。</div><div>2、市场预测能力和战略规划能力差距大。</div><div>提升计划：</div><div>1、增加信息源，积累大量基本数据信息。</div><div>2、提升思考能力，反思总结。</div><div>3、拓宽思路，锻炼规划能力，锻炼自己的分析能力提高预见能力</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7975,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492522794000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lasia","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPZjdCpPKAMDUgWoXUvkVcsqzWKUUicQdLDqSSXIAzKphVGZMibQL8RZHItR7wlTetH47SYQgiasgxu/0","content":"<p>上司的关键业务：满足客户需求，开发和稳定供应商。</p><p>如果我想也做业务，那就需要做相关提升。但目前在考虑换工作，所以暂不做此方面的计划。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7955,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492503196000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"<p>顶头上司的关键业务：</p><p>1.管理部门。</p><p>2.开拓和跟进大客户。</p><p>3.根据公司现状调整业务方向。</p><p>根据上司的关键业务，我认为自己一是学习和沟通，更全面地了解公司以及部门业务方向；二是发展更多的管理能力，通过PDCA管理项目和管理同事；三是向其他公司以及上司请求开脱客户相关知识，评估自己的核心资源，是否能够提供相应的客户价值。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7849,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492411075000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8hWCY4rsU5ic7YX8NSbKTQ1jqib9icr5cJBexUUicYhHibyRcicc1Y9Hxmc5hFqdxgaUNjiaBH4HIahUdE/0","content":"直接领导人关键业务:<div>项目计划把控，成本核算，风险分析，与客户的前期交流，团队管理</div><div><br></div><div>对比后发现我应该关注产品成本方面的信息和团队管理方面的知识。</div><div><br></div><div>提升计划:</div><div>1,了解每个项目的成本信息，思考可行的降成本方案。</div><div>2,学习团队管理</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7760,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492264110000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"好名字","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoPGEHL5t5mdvtbNw3mPvfT1b2Hz81247ETuKJ8JLlG6994qFzU8fxoVeJNWWrSKUWPzEcaRzJpwF/0","content":"line manager:沟通项目需求 把控项目进度 &nbsp;提报<div>myself:执行项目（进一步沟通项目细节，撰写计划书，问卷，访谈大纲，整理数据，撰写报告）</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7615,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492042214000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Elva","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoFaxYzCOkAgT6U2G0vGpXUa0F8N8eibrdQDFDpDsIQR0o4LFlkibaV2e9sqVQWTSnESkEN3QcQNcXz/0","content":"1. 规划申请费用用于每年，每季度，每月份的活动经费<div>2. 规划福建区所需要的销售人员</div><div>3. 制作审核活动经费报销资料</div><div>4. 培训，主持开会等</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6532,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491557234000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"\uD83D\uDC8DEileen\uD83D\uDD06","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6abalthMJiaYnoibZVuO5CvSR8HOKWNjhJyafcnkmAkvTZ9NZIu7ibtL0hZb0tFft1ZWlJB8cmhjzGuaQSxNldicib3T/0","content":"领导关键业务<div>审核单据，汇报财务数据给大老板，管理财务部财务人员</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7199,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491310475000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lanlan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","content":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【上司的关键业务】</p><p>1、经常性与潜在客户进行沟通，寻求合作机会；</p><p>2、与甲方沟通项目初步方案，为对方提供解决方案，达成项目合作；</p><p>3、处理项目人员部署和资源调度，项目任务的计划安排；定期召开项目例会，检查各项工作工作完成情况；部署项目结题工作，参加项目答辩；</p><p>4、协调人员完成项目总结和成果包装，部署团队宣传；</p><p>5、定期监督和检查供应商合作情况；</p><p>6、协调项目财务问题；</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【自己当前的关键业务】</p><p>1、针对项目进行详细设计，安排人员完成项目工作，推动项目进展；</p><p>2、解决项目中的关键技术问题；</p><p>3、客户反馈问题的解决；</p><p>4、产品交货工作部署；</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【对比和提升计划】</p><p>通过对比，发现与上司在关键业务方面的主要区别是：（1）自己与客户沟通太少，为客户直接提供初步解决方案比较少，因此无法促成项目合作；（2）了解更多的是项目的具体细节，但对全局把握不够，无法提供系统性的全局解决方案；（3）一些事务性工作没能布置给下属，导致自己经常纠缠于具体技术问题，无法发挥自己的管理优势，无法有更大的自我提升。</p><p></p><p>因此，具体的提升计划包括：（1）提高自己的口头表达能力，更多了解客户需求，增加与客户沟通的机会；（2）提高系统思维能力，经常性对项目进行全局性的思考和总结，锻炼提供全局解决方案的能力；（3）增强对团队的管理和人员协调能力，将具体任务布置下去，一方面解放自己，另一方面锻炼新人。<br></p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7139,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491218659000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"预算编制参与<div>成本控制</div><div>柔性运作与管理</div><div>部门建设</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7115,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491174358000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
